#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: simple-export-md.php
msgid "Simple Export to Markdown"
msgstr "Simple Export to Markdown"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: simple-export-md.php
msgid "https://github.com/sherer-pro/simple-export-md"
msgstr "https://github.com/sherer-pro/simple-export-md"

#. Description of the plugin
#: simple-export-md.php
msgid "Adds a Gutenberg panel “Export to Markdown” with buttons to download .md or copy Markdown to clipboard."
msgstr "Aggiunge un pannello Gutenberg «Esporta in Markdown» con pulsanti per scaricare .md o copiare Markdown negli appunti."

